### Test Percentage Deductions
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Create a Fixed Deduction (₱500 for everyone)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/deduction-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Uniform Fee Test",
  "description": "Fixed ₱500 uniform fee",
  "amount": 500,
  "calculationType": "FIXED",
  "isMandatory": false,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 2. Create a Percentage Deduction (20% of salary)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/deduction-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Health Insurance Test",
  "description": "20% of basic salary for health insurance",
  "amount": 0,
  "calculationType": "PERCENTAGE",
  "percentageValue": 20,
  "isMandatory": false,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 3. Get all deduction types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/deduction-types

###

### 4. Apply deduction to employees
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/deductions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deduction_types_id": "YOUR_DEDUCTION_TYPE_ID_HERE",
  "selectAll": true,
  "notes": "Testing percentage calculation"
}

###

### 5. View all deductions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/deductions

###
